foods.ingredients: PRE-BAKED GINGERBREAD: ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, ASCORBIC ACID, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), SUGAR, VEGETABLE OIL SHORTENING (PALM), MOLASSES, WATER, CINNAMON, LEAVENING (SODIUM BICARBONATE), GINGER, SALT, CARAMEL COLOR. PRE-MADE ICING: POWDERED SUGAR, WATER, VEGETABLE OILS (PALM, CANOLA), CORN SYRUP AND HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, MODIFIED CORNSTARCH, SALT, SOY MONO-AND DIGLYCERIDES, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, CITRIC ACID, POLYSORBATE 60, PRESERVATIVE - POTASSIUM SORBATE, COLOR (TITANIUM DIOXIDE). RED & WHITE PINWHEELS: SUGAR, CORN SYRUP, COLORS (TITANIUM DIOXIDE, FD&C RED 40 LAKE), NATURAL PEPPERMINT FLAVOR. MINI JELLIES: GLUCOSE SYRUP, SUGAR, MODIFIED CORNSTARCH, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, CITRIC ACID, COLORS (FD&C RED 40, FD&C YELLOW 5, FD&C YELLOW 6, FD&C BLUE 1). PUCKER UPS: DEXTROSE, MALTODEXTRIN, CALCIUM STEARATE, MALIC ACID, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, CONFECTIONER'S GLAZE, TAPIOCA DEXTRIN, CARNAUBA WAX, COLORS (FD&C YELLOW 5, FD&C YELLOW 6, FD&C YELLOW 5 LAKE, FD&C YELLOW 6 LAKE, FD&C RED 40, FD&C RED 40 LAKE, FD&C BLUE 1, FD&C BLUE 1 LAKE, TITANIUM DIOXIDE). MINI BEADS: DEXTROSE, GLUCOSE, MALTODEXTRIN, CALCIUM STEARATE, CITRIC ACID, MALIC ACID, TAPIOCA DEXTRIN, CONFECTIONER'S GLAZE, CARNAUBA WAX, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, COLOR (FD&C RED 3, FD&C RED 40, FD&C YELLOW 5, FD&C BLUE 1 LAKE, TITANIUM DIOXIDE). CANDY CANES: SUGARS, CORN SYRUP, PEPPERMINT OIL, COLORS (FD&C RED 40, FD&C RED 40 LAKE).
